	dprr:hasNoteText "Attempted to prosecute Volscius Fictor for false witness against K. Quinctius (Liv. 3.24.3-7, and 29.6; see 461). This version of the story assumes that Volscius was no longer a Tribune (cf. Val. Max.4.1.4)." ;
